{"hb72ab755g331cg42e3gb833g08ef17ece218": ["*Cazador. Your <i>Master</i>. You have to get back to him quickly. If you're late, he'll flay you. Again.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_AstarionHunger_IVB_SCO_Avatar_Choice.html", "4aa512aa-3a0a-7309-2508-7013e4a47939"], "hb77fb721g6b4bg4d8egabd2g2a3201508179": ["*What will he say when he finds you can walk in the sunlight and he can't?*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_AstarionHunger_IVB_SCO_Avatar_Choice.html", "548239ec-df79-f9b9-7876-9a6f53f2b179"], "hb1e200d6g363ag42afga1bag969c26b11fc5": ["*And then it dawns on you: if you're free to walk in daylight, can you be free of Cazador too?*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_AstarionHunger_IVB_SCO_Avatar_Choice.html", "5123a475-fb05-126f-2d87-5a3d032d5482"], "h07ffd80eg38d4g43e8g8fc6g0699a97cf824": ["*Free of his rules?*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_AstarionHunger_IVB_SCO_Avatar_Choice.html", "be1ab4c5-bae1-aa5e-3cf0-c28829ddcd6c"], "hc1f24ad9g3834g493dgaff6g5712b97a2cb0": ["'First, thou shalt not drink of the blood of thinking creatures.'", "2f1880e6-1297-4ca3-a79c-9fabc7f179d3", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_AstarionHunger_IVB_SCO_Avatar_Choice.html", "40c5946b-e797-6fc1-b6c2-8af07e65ff5b"], "h513cd95agc119g42cdgbecega47544019f63": ["*You look at your companions. Resting. Helpless. How badly do you need to know?*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_AstarionHunger_IVB_SCO_Avatar_Choice.html", "268f2d30-04bf-1a01-ee95-d44357c4ef48"], "h9bea1866gacdbg42fbg9729gc4178815e2fd": ["*You look at your companions. Sleeping. Helpless. How badly do you need to know?*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_AstarionHunger_IVB_SCO_Avatar_Choice.html", "268f2d30-04bf-1a01-ee95-d44357c4ef48"], "h25c97997g7236g4eefg93deg568d8f3dcb19": ["<i>Approach [GEN_PlayerName2_85df4a15-4d9b-4f68-0512-d104305d8dac].</i>", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_AstarionHunger_IVB_SCO_Avatar_Choice.html", "79dd33bd-4618-c9cf-ea1e-7f2c1d0ec486"], "h3a95b2c8g2c13g4739g9e6dgb3b79c5b2163": ["*You can smell the sweetness of his skin - hear the beat of his pulse...*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_AstarionHunger_IVB_SCO_Avatar_Choice.html", "30b8730c-1b1b-4d7b-4bf4-e044829076d8"], "h958b799eg04afg4d08gb72bg9e4ea7a841ef": ["<i>Bite down, careful not to disturb them.</i>", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_AstarionHunger_IVB_SCO_Avatar_Choice.html", "9ca0a1c6-6476-9c7e-1bc6-6fa22f447319"], "hc1d703ddg32f0g4fceg98c2g3687eb01cfcf": ["*Gasp*", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_AstarionHunger_IVB_SCO_Avatar_Choice.html", "9242b53f-ca95-c7e4-f845-c02336c957d0"], "hf8f7698eg448cg475dgab34g1ad5c33e0c86": ["*Gasp*", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_AstarionHunger_IVB_SCO_Avatar_Choice.html", "186b3a31-f2ae-0132-f878-63c0125614f6"], "hc88c4f13g4fc7g4da3g96ecg0c8c914f0d26": ["*Blood gushes into your mouth. You can feel it filling the maw inside you - filling your soul.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_AstarionHunger_IVB_SCO_Avatar_Choice.html", "3cfc45f9-fc4a-971b-7a6c-72065450a66f"], "h70119a7cgda2fg4e40gbb80gef9a3e6ae24a": ["<i>Stop and pull away.</i>", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_AstarionHunger_IVB_SCO_Avatar_Choice.html", "657bf401-e72b-c719-e924-0ddbdac0d1e5"], "h1949e457gd06dg4619gb427gc9e7c43dcab7": ["*You fall back, glorious blood coating your throat.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_AstarionHunger_IVB_SCO_Avatar_Choice.html", "01fdd1a8-c9cf-5278-a6c7-b23345d01790"], "h8526c16eg0e9eg4ab7ga5cage7d43959b067": ["*You creep back to your bed with a full belly and singing heart. For the first time in centuries, you feel happy.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_AstarionHunger_IVB_SCO_Avatar_Choice.html", "5bf4a56f-9d16-f6f3-e77f-8992354185f0"], "hf279958dge324g4119gb6edg3f0c76a15f91": ["*You try to wrench your head back, but your jaw refuses to obey.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_AstarionHunger_IVB_SCO_Avatar_Choice.html", "fc157211-59fa-8319-d387-2e40dd6ea647"], "hccad264eg8e2fg4d01gb5c0gdc89afc55a93": ["*You drink and drink and drink. Until, without even a whimper, it's all over.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_AstarionHunger_IVB_SCO_Avatar_Choice.html", "50581ca9-d802-499f-23be-8e2ee796a719"], "h76f25d23g98d7g4afegbbbag8c35351d264b": ["*You try to wrench your head back, but your jaw refuses to obey.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_AstarionHunger_IVB_SCO_Avatar_Choice.html", "23e0e044-02cd-bd05-f2e4-cb05137dabb5"], "h374db35eg464ag4d1cgb32fg15db5024e768": ["*You drink and drink and drink. Until, without even a whimper, it's all over.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_AstarionHunger_IVB_SCO_Avatar_Choice.html", "9b7587ec-ef2a-29c4-5e44-31ba502dbc9b"], "h9f86e31bgc466g4bbbg927eg6433eec60b2f": ["*You try to wrench your head back, but your jaw refuses to obey.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_AstarionHunger_IVB_SCO_Avatar_Choice.html", "476cb535-15b2-59d8-d515-f1c1dea24d3b"], "h0003edd4g9ae0g4246gbf0dg0c404ffc6585": ["*You drink and drink and drink. Until, without even a whimper, it's all over.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_AstarionHunger_IVB_SCO_Avatar_Choice.html", "85b099b2-d857-c550-f0d0-74789f244096"], "h58c71c83geed8g4dadg9859g4784ceaa991e": ["<i>Keep drinking.</i>", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_AstarionHunger_IVB_SCO_Avatar_Choice.html", "bde7ecad-5752-c496-f955-a1f2f8fe7326"], "h3068a9a8gd3a5g44b8ga090gd54ed42ebd33": ["*Gasp*", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb